{"text": "If we compare it to the famous fishing planet, this game is its minimalist version. Pros: Simple interface and very easy to get used to Does not ask for much requirement Multiplayer for tournaments with an active community In-game currency obtained through quests and daily challenges Various maps and locations Fast fishing without many waiting times Various minigames to obtain rewards Change of schedules that influence the day and night cycles It is FREE TO PLAY, you do not lose anything by downloading it and trying it, it weighs little Cons. Anarchic movement of the rod when casting Not being able to see other fishermen, which creates a feeling of loneliness Minimalist chat without channel separation Faulty and ineffective friend system in the game In summary ... good fishing game to have and access daily to take a relaxed hour or more depends on your days, ask for little, so the pc is luxurious, it is highly recommended if you like simple fishing games. ", "voted_up": true, "early_access": false}
