{"text": "Slowly but surely, I got to writing a review for Euro Truck Simulator 2, a trucker simulator. Why slow? Because it took a little time to understand the game. Quite good, very pleasant game, quite atmospheric and interesting. I think that everyone knows about its meaning. We travel across Europe and deliver goods. There are some interesting things to do with building your campaign, hiring drivers and making big bucks. But this, frankly, is not very exciting. For most of the game we will have to work as a bum mercenary. And that's not bad, I can tell you. If everything was the way it is in this game, I would dream of becoming a truck driver from early childhood, and most importantly, I would fulfill this dream. This game shows the best life of a simple trucker: he gets decently, fines are low, foreign cars are comfortable, agile and in general, it's nice to sit in them, and what kind of roads are there ... Well, yes, 10 times better than ours. I really like the option with radio stations, because they are real, moreover, the authors tried to include completely different ones in this list: classical, metal, folk, rock, jazz, as they say, for every taste. Radio is really an important aspect of the atmosphere of this game. Speaking about it, I would like to add only one thing: it seems to me that they did not tighten up a little, did not bring in any interesting adventures, any accidents or road accidents. Everything looks too perfect, and this is the main problem of all simulators, it's like in The Sims - a life simulator, everyone is always too funny and funny, but this is unrealistic. So here too, we drive regularly, we earn money, we drive badly, we earn less money and end up buying ourselves a truck, but up to this point it is interesting to play, namely to be a mercenary, but then? Does the game become so interesting after you buy yourself a truck? And then on a new one, create a new campaign and download the character. Yes, download it, friends. The pumping element is present not only in the truck, but also in the driver, there are many different perks for which we spend points once a level. In general, it is interesting to play, as for the purpose of this game, it is more likely to guide the player in a relaxed and calm state. I don't know about you, but I literally fall asleep playing this game. No tension, no bad thoughts, complete relaxation, well, if, of course, you don't drive at full speed. Thus, one day I fell asleep while playing this game. But this is not bad, in no case is it, on the contrary, it shows that the game was a success. Of course, you won't play it for a long time, because it gets boring, but once a week it is a pleasure to play it. And then, some drive for hours in this game, but that's what anyone is interested in. The game has fulfilled its task 100%, who says that it is boring, but what should be a game about simulation of the life of a trucker? This is not our show, is it? This game is exactly what it should be. This is why I give her a 9 out of 10. ", "voted_up": true, "early_access": false}
