{"text": "Terraria is a 2D sandbox with RPG elements, including multiple classes, a countless number of bosses and enemies, as well as over 3000 items ranging from different types of armour, weapons, gadgets, and potions; all which will leave you playing for hours on end. In my opinion, it is by far the best indie game I've ever played. My first run of Terraria went beyond my expectations and proved to be an amazing experience, and it was even better since I played it along with friends. If you are buying this on sale, it only costs $5 and you are getting a full game with all the DLC for free. The developers have done a great job maintaining Terraria over the past years and have never failed to satisfy it's playerbase, which can be reflected by it's positive feedback. I highly recommend this game if you do not have it in your Steam library yet. Stop reading reviews and buy the game already! ~ 10/10 ", "voted_up": true, "early_access": false}
