{"text": "Hello everyone, this is my review of the game Grand Theft Auto: Vice City. Events unfold in 1986. Tommy Vercetti, released after 15 years in prison, goes to Vice City on the instructions of his boss Sonny Forelli to control the drug deal, but it breaks down during the course and all the people with whom Tommy arrived on the deal are killed and Tommy has no choice but to escape and not allow himself to be shot, after Sonny finds out about the failure, he demands to return the money and goods, and this is how the criminal life of the charismatic mafia Tommy Vercetti begins. Well, I would like to start with the graphics, because, unlike GTA 3, it has become much better, now everything is filled with colors and not as dull and gloomy as in GTA 3, plus in general the whole game is now not so square and soapy, in general graphics are on top and pleasing to the eye. Sunny Miami, beautiful bright graphics + excellent radio stations, all this gives you a complete immersion in the plot and you get full pleasure from the game. The coolest thing about this game is the plot, which is why I advise everyone to play this game, the charismatic protagonist and very interesting missions from simple murders to parkour on a motorcycle on the rooftops makes this game one of the best in terms of plot from the GTA series. Compared to GTA 3, this one is better in everything, more varied missions, not only murders and transporting whores from one point to another, but for example promoting a porn studio, helicopter missions, selling ice cream or distributing leaflets by plane over the entire city, and much more. the same radio stations became much cooler, for example, the same songs by Michael Jackson, and much more, the game also became more interactive, it became possible to go to a police station or a club, or in the same shopping center you can also buy your own houses, factories and enterprises for promotion of their business, more weapons were also added to the game, just like in GTA 3, limbs fly off from shots from people, the physics of cars is simply divine compared to GTA 3, now the cars do not turn so sharply and do not start to smoke from two hits. In the game, it is also impossible to simultaneously aim and move. Personally, I liked the game and I recommend it to everyone, at least not because of the graphics, but because of the plot ", "voted_up": true, "early_access": false}
