{"text": "Spiral Knights (SK for short) is a massively multiplayer online MMORPGs (massively multiplayer online game) that brings everyone together. It's like creating a virtual world. With a player taking on the role of one in that virtual world It was originally developed by Three Rings Design and then distributed by Sega, later transferred to Gray Havens, a company of the Three Rings former employee group. Let's take care of it all. The gameplay of Spiral Knights is a top-down view from the top, with the essence of being action-adventure. It is said to be similar or comparable to The Legend of Zelda: Four Swords Adventures, but SK is 3D, not 2D like Zelda. You can play collaboratively with other people. At the heart of the gameplay will be dabble in dungeons with many kinds of monsters. Various puzzle mechanisms Including traps at various points in the dungeon The game does not have a leveling system for characters. Only full heat will be required to complete the Forge, which will allow you to level up your equipment (weapons, shields, armor), which requires a Fire Crystal for each Forge. At every level up, there are 3 forge levels: low / medium / max. Each level uses a different number of Fire Crystal, the better the level. The more you use the more. Likelihood of Forge success too + Intuitive gameplay There are story quests, daily quests and arcade play, dungeon setting design that looks good, weapons, shields, armor. Various in-game items are very diverse, and versatile abilities. Of all 3 types of pets, dressed up cool and pretty with costumes and accessories, sitting looking for cool items in the Auction House shop, decorating various parts in the guild house, how to fight each boss It came better than expected and the background music is beautiful. All of these are the strengths that make the game so exciting and fun to play - the disadvantages of the game. First of all, the game has been stopping to update anything new for a long time, but only the same events that cycle according to each season, no Asian servers. Of course, if Thai people go for lag, it is definitely easy. But it can be rubbed, but not very good, at present there are no more than 500 players in this game, there are many enemies in the game, but most of them just change the color according to the element. In addition, the attack pattern is the same repeatedly, the PVP is passive, personally I think that going down the dungeon with friends and others is more fun, imbalance of some daily quests. Which is too difficult and the story makes the quest no fun This includes a mid-level Forge imbalance that fails easily despite the 70 - 75% success rate and the disappointing peak of the game +/-. The game is semi-To-Win if not. If you can pay You will have to spend time farming, money, Grinding Farms. So brutal and very boring. Because of having to do things over and over for a very, very, very long period of time before being able to get rich against the person who spay Plus, you may feel lonely at times because people do not already have it. But if you are a person who likes to do things over and over again and have fun and never get bored. You will be able to buy a lot of the stuff currently available in the game in a very short time. The peak of this game From what I have observed It is inevitable that the costumes and accessories are pretty expensive to stand in front of the Auction House shop because there are more people than people building rooms to go down to dungeons. It's really like this. Probably because the gameplay is going around and over and over again, no new updates. I'm not really surprised why I think the pinnacle of this game is to put together expensive costumes and beautiful accessories to stand in front of the Auction House, something that I am very disappointed with at the peak of This game, because it has nothing to do with the core of the gameplay. It's just a small part, but much more outstanding than the main gameplay. The most rewarding point of this game. I think it's about Achievements, because few people can unlock the extremely difficult and 100% Achievements. I recommend playing for fun or for achievement. Just enough, this is enough. If you want to play seriously I think there are many other good games online than this one. ", "voted_up": false, "early_access": false}
