{"text": "Plot. The plot is ... but yes, I forgot, it's not here. It's a web browser game. Well, if it's simple, somewhere in a distant galaxy, little robots are fighting between each other for candy, and thanks to magic paper clips, these robots improve their armor and other parts of their body. Karochi, no fantasy. Moving on to the gameplay. Gameplay. Here the developer took all the best from different games (Quake 3, they even took a copy of one map, I say, there is no imagination to come up with something of their own.) And something like that happened. You kill robots, you win, you get paper clips. You can kill with different guns. But most of the guns you will use and take only to complete achievements. There are several game modes that are typical of other games in this genre. There was no more strength left to come up with something of my own. Balance and earnings in the game. This is where the developers show their alternative side of their greed. In order to upgrade your character, you will have to enter the game every day so as not to lose the bonus, complete achievements and increase the level. All. That's all the earnings, and in order to pump up to maximum armor, you will have to invest in the game. I figured it out for a long time, it comes out about 10,000 rubles. Where will a student get so much money? That's right, he will take from his parents, who have long wanted to get rid of their annoying son. It was even earlier, they introduced GOLDEN STAPLES. Well, this is when there is no time to play and get into the big league, but there is 100 rubles, which I have been saving up and saving for school lunches for a whole month. Therefore, it is up to you to decide: either invest in a game to get into a cool super-duper clan and all the children were afraid of you, or to shoot robots heads off all day and night. Moving on to the graph. Grafon. Oooh, the developers did a great job. Turning on the Ultra-grafon mode, your game will stop working, unless, of course, you have an expensive computer. Therefore, all the boys play at the minimum salary, but if you want brightness, just increase the brightness on the screen, and not change the graphics settings. And so the graphics are made in children's styles. Features of the game. Hmm ... well, yes, there are game modes, opportunities to complete achievements, a large selection of paints, leagues, exclusive items, grenades, 3 classes of robots. But all this did not exist before and was well played without it. And what is all this for then? I will answer you - so that with \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 you can spend the cherished 100 rubles, as Likhova likes to do it. Let's summarize the results. We have a game that is ready to give you all the delights of the game for money, or for a long period of the game. Over time, you will get tired of the monotony of the game. The only thing that saves the game is tournaments and KV, which the players arrange among themselves. So schoolchildren from all over the country find out who is the coolest gold cap. I do not recommend this game to rogues and those who like to pass the time for a couple of hours. All this is Chivalry: Medieval Warfare! 10 out of 10 not happy with Gabe. ", "voted_up": false, "early_access": false}
