vigator. For example, I don\u2019t want to go along the arrows, but I like to lay the route myself, whatever I want. 7. But this is a complaint to our legalizers. Terrible subtitles. Not only are they small, they are also shown in a solid block a few frames before. Change 4 or 5 pictures, but the subtitles do not change. I personally would like the information to come as the characters pronounce the words. Yes, they didn't even translate the news on the radio, the simplest thing, well 8. I'll just say that a lot of chips were licked off from GTA, Assassin's Creed, Watch Dogs. 9. Small settings menu, spoiled brutality and charisma of Vito, it feels like it's not him, but his clone and much, much more. All the disadvantages cannot be enumerated. And money scattered everywhere, even on the toilet cistern, causes nothing but tears of laughter. I could close my eyes to many bloopers if at least something was done perfectly in the game. But alas. Is that the very atmosphere of the game, and even then it is somehow full of holes. You can play, of course, the game, but the pleasure, as from the previous parts, will clearly not be. It's so easy to kill time and that's it. I recommend it only out of respect for the line of games itself. Mafia 3 should definitely be nominated for Disappointment of the Year. I was waiting for this game the most, I liked the mafia first and even more, I was just delighted, mafia 2. I expected a great continuation of the story of Vito and Joe, but I got this ... I'm very disappointed, the developers just killed a fan in me ... The final score from me is 3.5 / 10. Terrible mediocrity and disappointment for all fans of the cult mafia. ", "voted_up": false, "early_access": false}
