{"text": "Update: Game keeps getting worse and worse over time as R* implements more and more things that are catered towards short term gains (toys for PvP-addicted kids with access to their parents' credit cards) while completely disregarding quality of life and features for those people who made the series popular and well-esteemed in the first place. The updates keep getting lazier and lazier, more and more broken and unbalanced. As of today, the release of Arena Wars, it personally is my last straw for the time being. ", "voted_up": false, "early_access": false}
