{"text": "Description: Puzzler World 2 - A collection of various puzzles and crosswords numbering 1200 pieces. The difficulty of the levels is different, but basically everything is very simple, difficulties can only be the last riddles, and even then hardly. The game is completely in English. As a sequel, the game, unlike the original, brought with it various innovations, in the form of additional games and an updated reward for completing levels. Pros: \u00a5 Many different puzzles. \u00a5 A system of hints that we get for completing riddles and which must be spent wisely. \u00a5 Roulette rewards after completing levels. Disadvantages: \u00a5 Unlike the first part - the choice of any level from the start has been abolished. \u00a5 Riddles are too simple. \u00a5 Achievements are too easy. If the game is designed for more than 100 hours of completion, then achievements can be taken in half an hour or an hour. \u00a5 Again, there are no Japanese crosswords (this is generally sadness-sadness-longing). \u00a5 Link a pix is \u200b\u200bthe best thing about the first part. They took it and screwed it up ... We made the map of the screen enlarged and now the decision is not that inconvenient, but extremely unpleasant. \u00a5 Do not change the screen resolution (and it is very small). Game essence: The long-awaited sequel to last year's hit on PC, Puzzler World 2 brings in more puzzles, new games, exciting rewards and a new \"Mastery Mode\". Created by the same team that worked on the original Puzzler World, a team that was able to change and improve every element of the game. With a revised selection of puzzles and mini-games, a new game mode, and a reward system, Puzzler World 2 takes the franchise to the next level! At the end of each puzzle, a bonus game opens, in which the player can receive a completely new random prize. Players can spin the wheel and watch. what prize they can get. Players can win hint tokens, which can then be used by them in difficult situations. Puzzler World 2 also allows players to unlock a special \"Master Mode\" that challenges powerful players. Key features: Over 1200 new puzzles and minigames from leading puzzle game creators - PML Play a variety of puzzles such as: Wordsearch, Fitword, Sudoku, Crossword, Hide and Seek, Link-a-Pix, Backwords, Silhouette and Pieceword Unlock additional mini-games - Picture Quiz, Splitwords, Chain Letters, Color-In, Sum-Up, Jigsaw, Hangman, Chain Letters and more! Bottom line: Compared to the first part, everything turned out much worse. Why change something that already worked great? Well, we decided to do the second part, add new games and that's it. Why touch the old? But no ... They spoiled everything and at the same time brought almost nothing new. From the graphic side, for sure. If I passed the first part 100%, then I got achievements and forgot. I do not recommend it. My rating: 4/10 ", "voted_up": false, "early_access": false}
